{"tid":2319198,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聯合國斥港府濫捕 促維護公平審判","createTime":"2020-12-10T02:25:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T02:46:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"83b97f83e56c26ff0a2a69c3750a9f666253e5bb","tid":2319198,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:25:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201210/SP24SM33DFBNFKN6YOOOZREMPA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201210%2FSP24SM33DFBNFKN6YOOOZREMPA%2F&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYptekL701Gi2Y7kfdl15EDb4%3D&h=ee913731\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201210%2FSP24SM33DFBNFKN6YOOOZREMPA%2F&h=7eedb29b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201210/SP24SM33DFBNFKN6YOOOZREMPA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n聯合國斥港府濫捕 促維護公平審判<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tNwG3o4yuGmgpJ_QIaBgOGFcTo4=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/37GGH4AGLRBFVPQAQBLVBCWSZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtNwG3o4yuGmgpJ_QIaBgOGFcTo4%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F37GGH4AGLRBFVPQAQBLVBCWSZQ.jpg&h=caec08c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■聯合國人權事務高級專員巴切萊特敦促港司法當局維護司法正當程序。路透社<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方前日拘捕八名民立派人士，指他們涉組織或參與七一遊行、煽惑他人參與未經批准集結等三宗罪，引起國際社會關注。聯合國人權事務高級專員巴切萊特（Michelle Bachelet）昨開腔，表示關注香港迅速縮窄的公民和民主空間，敦促香港司法當局維護司法正當程序和公正審判權利。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：林鄭：冀後世記得我是為港人的特首<br />\n<br />\n香港警方前日拘捕前立法會議員胡志偉、梁國雄、朱凱廸、民陣召集人陳皓桓及東區區議員曾健成等八人，指他們涉嫌今年7月1日煽惑他人參與、組織及參與未經批准集結，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指社運人士入罪掀寒蟬效應<br />\n<br />\n巴切萊特昨在瑞士日內瓦總部記者會上回應，「近日被定罪的社運人士曾參與去年的示威活動，令（港人）行使基本自由方面，形成更廣泛寒蟬效應的風險」。她亦對新疆一連串嚴重侵犯人權行為表示關注，希望其團隊明年上半年前能到中國為她到訪北京做準備。<br />\n<br />\n國際特赦組織等22個人權組織，去年11月曾向巴切萊特發公開信，要求聯合國公開譴責香港政府系統性侵犯和平集會自由和言論自由權利，並譴責港警不必要和過度使用武力的行為，她同月在《南華早報》撰文，促請港府採取措施建立市民信心，包括針對警方過度使用武力的報告，進行獨立及由法官領導的公正調查等。"},{"pid":"439a5d2720fd091c8b4b5aecd1845b9408ea3ea6","tid":2319198,"uid":230530,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:25:48.000Z","msg":"公平？乜嚟架？食得架？"},{"pid":"2cdf41586a1c33186de28b89b1af84ad0514758d","tid":2319198,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e93b77c482c1a1475168444b40360e616660626","tid":2319198,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a11af2ec49fb4c5564b4ddf6011cbaaab05aed","tid":2319198,"uid":265486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:37:56.000Z","msg":"仲唔快啲屌埋聯合國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"433e0ec0e80c601e536d20e48072d9fcccafe55a","tid":2319198,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:43:13.000Z","msg":"選擇性地：<br />\n<br />\n執法拘捕<br />\n控告<br />\n審訊<br />\n不批保釋<br />\n判刑<br />\n<br />\n對親政權者，就用最寬鬆<br />\n對反對者，就用最嚴果套<br />\n<br />\n都係叫「依法」"},{"pid":"9002d0b2bab957aa7366b647a7fa2a5a9b34a8df","tid":2319198,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:44:32.000Z","msg":"雖然仲慢過IE<br />\n但遲到好過唔到"},{"pid":"30ec63b2b67ae70fbd84a34f3d14f25249fcfbcb","tid":2319198,"uid":259812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:46:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}